722362f-a.text:
Park Avenue, east side, from 87th to 86th Streets, showing No. 1049 Park Avenue, an apartment house about four years old. The old 3-story frame No. 1047 together with the small builcings to the corner of 86th Street, is shortly to be demolished. Compure
